            <td width="100%">
            <div id="customerLogo">&nbsp;</div>
            <div id="messagebody" style="font: 12px verdana">&nbsp;</div>
            <div id="Signature" style="font: 12px verdana">
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Hi, </font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">I have an immediate requirement opening for a <span style="background: yellow">Sr. Java Developer position; this is a 3-4 months contract</span>. I would appreciate if you could send your updated word format resume along with best contact details ASAP.</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara; background: yellow; font-size: 14pt"><font size="3">Candidates can be from India or from the US who can go to India, expenses of travel and accommodation would be taken care by Client.</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: Candara; color: blue"><font size="3">Start&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : ASAP</font></span></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: Candara; color: blue"><font size="3">&nbsp;Location&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : Noida, India</font></span></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><span style="font-family: Candara; color: blue"><font size="3">&nbsp;Duration&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; : 3-4 months.</font></span></strong></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">We are looking for Sr Assoc Tech who has good technical design experience - creating design documents, creating high level design etc. </font></span></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><u><span style="font-family: Candara; color: blue"><font size="3">Please find below some more details:</font></span></u></strong></div>
            <ul type="disc" style="margin-top: 0in">
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Strong experience mainly in Java/JEE</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Good experience designing relatively complex Web based applications.</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Comfortable with Design Patterns, Class Design using UML, Database design using ERDs</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Experience of Spring MVC, Spring Webflow, Spring IOC, and Hibernate.</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Experience of Websphere App Server and Oracle DB.</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Experience of SOAP based web services and related things such as WSDL etc.</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Ability to communicate fluently</font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Good if has had recognitions and accolades from client</font></span></li>
            </ul>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><strong><u><span style="font-family: Candara; color: blue"><font size="3">Required skills and Responsibilities:</font></span></u></strong></div>
            <ul type="disc" style="margin-top: 0in">
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Candidates need to have a good design experience on reasonably large projects over a relatively long period of time. </font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">They should have design leadership experience and conceptual clarity apart from a good knowledge of technology. </font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">One way to test this would be to find out how comfortable the candidate is with design patterns (GoF, MVC etc.) and how clearly he can explain them. </font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Another way would be to see how comfortable they are with UML (i.e. not only class diagrams but the other diagrams as well) and ERDs. </font></span></li>
                <li style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><span style="font-family: Candara"><font size="3">Also ask them how long have they been on designer roles and what was the size/complexity of the modules they have been responsible for.</font></span></li>
            </ul>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></div>
            <div style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt"><a name="_MailAutoSig"><span style="font-family: Cambria; color: black; font-size: 10pt"><font size="3">Thanks/Regards,</font></span></a></div>
